  <summary date="2021-09-03T19:24:29Z" status="Introduced in House">Department of Defense Burn Pits Health Provider Training Act

This bill requires the Department of Defense to train its medical providers on the potential health effects of burn pits, which are areas used for burning solid waste in open air without equipment.</summary>
